# PAKE+ System Commit Message Template
# 
# Format: <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Types:
#   feat:     A new feature
#   fix:      A bug fix
#   docs:     Documentation changes
#   style:    Code style changes (formatting, etc)
#   refactor: Code refactoring
#   test:     Adding or updating tests
#   chore:    Maintenance tasks
#   security: Security-related changes
#
# Security Checklist:
# [ ] No secrets or credentials included
# [ ] No sensitive configuration data
# [ ] No API keys or tokens
# [ ] No database REDACTED_SECRETs
# [ ] No private keys or certificates
#
# Example:
# security(auth): implement secure credential management
#
# - Replace hardcoded REDACTED_SECRETs with environment variables
# - Add secrets management infrastructure
# - Update .gitignore to exclude sensitive files
#
